Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二  各式各样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是旅行的礼物也不尽是物品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如照片  或者印象深刻的回忆之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  照片的话拍了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:24.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（包子铺）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:25.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（京都年糕）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:26.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（京都果冻）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:27.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（塔式巧克力）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物…而且全是吃的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法全买下…就只能拍下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐真的买了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  看起来很好吃…顺手就买了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小澪好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是保质期都是今天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啦  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:01:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超过保质期的话  里面就会变得湿嗒嗒粘糊糊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在今天全部吃完才行

